                    <p class="card-text text-muted small line-clamp-3">Bu yıl mutfaklarda beyaz Carrara mermeri mi yoksa koyu renkli granitler mi moda? İç mimarların seçimi.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="text-uppercase text-dark fw-bold text-decoration-none small" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Devamını Oku <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ms-1"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm hover-card">
                <div class="overflow-hidden" style="height: 250px;">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1564013799919-ab600027ffc6?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" class="card-img-top w-100 h-100 object-fit-cover" alt="Blog 3">
                </div>
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <span class="badge bg-black rounded-0 mb-2">Tarihçe</span>
                    <h5 class="card-title fw-bold mt-2" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Carrara Mermerinin Tarihi</h5>
